# HSM collector integer value conformance.
# These cases pin the shared payload shape for the first portable sensor slice.

int_value_zero|create_collector
int_value_zero|create_int_sensor|contract/value/zero
int_value_zero|start
int_value_zero|add_int|0|0|Ok|zero
int_value_zero|expect_sent_count|1
int_value_zero|expect_payload_contains|0|"Value":0

